com.alexgilleran.icesoap.envelope.impl

Class BaseSOAPEnvelope

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.alexgilleran.icesoap.xml.impl.XMLObjectBase
      • com.alexgilleran.icesoap.xml.impl.XMLNodeBase
        • com.alexgilleran.icesoap.xml.impl.XMLParentNodeImpl
          • com.alexgilleran.icesoap.envelope.impl.BaseSOAPEnvelope
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SOAPEnvelope, XMLElement, XMLNode, XMLParentNode
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaseSOAP11Envelope, BaseSOAP12Envelope

    public abstract class BaseSOAPEnvelope
extends XMLParentNodeImpl
implements SOAPEnvelope
    Base implementation of SOAPEnvelope, containing logic contained by both SOAP 1.1 and SOAP 1.2 envelopes - when creating envelopes, use BaseSOAP11Envelope or BaseSOAP12Envelope depending on your SOAP version.
    Author:
    Alex Gilleran
